A [[Missions#Other Mission|Mission]] offered at [[stations]].

General difficulty: Moderate to Hard 

You will need to make the pilot of the specified ship bail so you can claim it or board for bigger ships. 

What you will need: 

* M3/M4 - smaller target. Don't shoot too much or you'll destroy him! 
* M6 & TP or M7M - necessary to board the target. 

What you will find: 

* M3/M4 - smaller targets 
* M6/M7 - bigger targets. You need to board these.


